05:03.568 --> 05:05.268
Even the most skilled trapeze artists

05:05.270 --> 05:06.502
use safety nets.

05:06.504 --> 05:10.440
Ugh. Is that the lame analogy she used?

05:10.442 --> 05:13.609
Why would I take guidance from her, anyway?

05:13.611 --> 05:15.510
She went to UConn.

05:15.512 --> 05:18.213
How can you be so snobby,
stubborn, and seductive

05:18.215 --> 05:19.647
all at the same time?

05:19.649 --> 05:21.183
Lots of practice.

05:21.185 --> 05:23.085
Mouse, I respect your chutzpah,

05:23.087 --> 05:25.153
