making a bad decision.

05:25.155 --> 05:26.521
You know the word "chutzpah"?

05:26.523 --> 05:29.591
Yeah. The guidance
counselor taught it to me.

05:31.659 --> 05:35.262
In New York City, a true
sign of a serious relationship

05:35.264 --> 05:38.332
