06:16.770 --> 06:18.237
No!

06:19.671 --> 06:21.506
Thank you.

06:22.608 --> 06:24.575
Weaver's words are haunting
my every waking moment.

06:24.577 --> 06:26.544
Actually, my every sleeping moment, too,

06:26.546 --> 06:28.712
